Box 60, 122 6th Street, Carrollton, KY 41008 Office Hours are 8 a.m. to 5 p.m. Mon, Tue, Thur & Fri, and 9 a.m. to 5 p.m. on Wed, 19118=Girl Scout Troop Nos. 306 and 1153 will host a father-daughter dance on Friday, May 3 from 6-8 p.m. at Camp Kysoc.
